Invocation Name: forty weeks
des:
The Forty Weeks skill has answers to your pregnancy questions from real parents’ experiences. From trying to get pregnant to coming home with your new baby, get facts, tips and answers to questions you were too embarrassed to ask. No pregnancy is perfect, and no topic is off-limits.
 
Visit nopregnancyisperfect.com to find additional answers, watch real couples share real stories about pregnancy, and much more.
 
This skill is for educational purposes only. It does not provide medical advice, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
